Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:04.75,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{But no cheating on me.}Nhưng đừng chơi hoa bẻ cành đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:07.02,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,S-Saki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:14.67,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{Did you think I would do such a thing?}Em nghĩ anh sẽ làm những chuyện như thế ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:16.76,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Naoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:19.76,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry for making you worry!}Xin lỗi vì đã làm em lo lắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.32,0:01:26.17,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{I'll love you even more so you'll never \Nhave to worry about me cheating on you!}Anh sẽ yêu em nhiều hơn nữa đến khi \N em không còn nghĩ đến việc anh sẽ bỏ em.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:27.44,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Huh? Wait...}Hả? Đợi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:29.10,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{H-H-Hey!}N-N-Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.10,0:01:29.94,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Let me go!}Buôn em ra đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:31.94,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{I love you, Saki-chan!}Saki-chan! Anh yêu em!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:34.81,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Let me go!}buôn em ra đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:36.12,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Saki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:38.09,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{Feel my love!}Em nhận được chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:39.14,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{I feel it!}Em nhận rồi! 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.14,0:01:39.84,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{You feel it?}Có chắc không?
