Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:34.00,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Oh, damn it!}Ôi, trời ơi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:37.96,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Bring it on!}Tới đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.51,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Anyway, I'm going now.}Vậy, Em đi đây.
